Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.35,1:58:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\bord0\shad0\1c&HE0E0E0\an8}好萊塢有數百人被列入黑名單
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.02,1:58:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\bord0\shad0\1c&HE0E0E0\an8}而全美則有數千人受到不白之冤
